{"tid":2505320,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"喺Uniqlo被指使用新疆棉之際，香港分部公關竟然作出如此舉動！？","createTime":"2021-04-26T13:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:51:47.000Z","uid":219969,"like":97,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cc7eeadd76884cba64291d75c3362201c90d86","tid":2505320,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"Uniqlo母公司：我哋政治中立，新疆人權問題唔答！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於中國新疆維吾爾族的人權問題時，迅銷董事長兼公司社長的柳井正回答：<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「在政治方面會抱持中立的立場。恕不評論。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQfdUFdxLR3WgUVffkjwEXWW7sFZupdcwEpbSbtQ15pWa?filename=Z47Uk2x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ47Uk2x.jpg&h=586f117c&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210410/AE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210410%2FAE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=4b70c2f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210410%2FAE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q&h=830d194b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210410/AE7EUAZYR5C2RDTIC6GWTIMS2Q</a> <br />\n<br />\nUniqlo香港，都係「政治中立」，新聞審查問題唔答，假新聞問題唔答！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賺錢至上，繼續搵TVB藝人賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">🚫 Uniqlo 🚫</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/uniqlo.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funiqlo.hk&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=97cd11c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/uniqlo.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/nj4QxQXW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2Fnj4QxQXW&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=8223349c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/nj4QxQXW</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbqL9ZhfdkmFdAFPwZ6oXJ6ffH3wwdTzRxw2MQQLDfnMQ?filename=7QxhiML.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QxhiML.jpg&h=fbf52867&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98955eb0b1144b8a8c7a9cd5aa869fb22d75598a","tid":2505320,"uid":219969,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:15:38.000Z","msg":"法國數個非政府組織與一名受害維吾爾倖存者今天向巴黎法院控訴4間跨國服裝巨擘，指控他們從新疆維吾爾人被迫勞動中獲利。控方律師表示，這是歐洲各國一系列控訴的開始。<br />\n<br />\n控訴書中，Inditex集團被控與新疆的重要紡織製造商有密切聯繫，但Inditex否認此說法。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">UNIQLO則是被控使用布料來自新疆以及可能有成千上萬維吾爾被迫勞動的安徽地區</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104100013.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202104100013.aspx&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=d67f8e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104100013.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【TVB戰線懶人區】<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">【紅媒金主】一田百貨</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/3LsKI7y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpili.app%2Fpg%2F3LsKI7y&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B66npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=b66fee4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pili.app/pg/3LsKI7y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2503923/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2503923/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">【紅媒金主】溶腩酵素(御藥堂)</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://pili.app/pg/1py3